    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039360/extras/42fbb1cb8e0fc377c909f4ff50ad4989.poster.avif?t=1732526354\" width=800 height=426 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039360/extras/42fbb1cb8e0fc377c909f4ff50ad4989.webm?t=1732526354\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039360/extras/42fbb1cb8e0fc377c909f4ff50ad4989.mp4?t=1732526354\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Luna's Diary is a 3D rhythm Platformer game that uses rhythms from multiple instruments, not just one rhythm.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Luna's Diary</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Falling into the world in the picture diary, Luna has to collect pieces of memory by exploring the world in the diary to regain her memory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Rhythmic Platforming and Music-centric Design</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039360/extras/946db8de2aa352eda559ab36c5caa190.poster.avif?t=1732526354\" width=280 height=156 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039360/extras/946db8de2aa352eda559ab36c5caa190.webm?t=1732526354\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039360/extras/946db8de2aa352eda559ab36c5caa190.mp4?t=1732526354\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Proceed with Platforming to the rhythm of several instruments. As Luna regains her memory, new instruments begin to play, and objects on the stage wake up and start working in response to the melody. Move forward, completing your memory and music.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039360/extras/49c52cc78d6036afcf7d8fc8217dfa0d.poster.avif?t=1732526354\" width=280 height=156 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039360/extras/49c52cc78d6036afcf7d8fc8217dfa0d.webm?t=1732526354\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039360/extras/49c52cc78d6036afcf7d8fc8217dfa0d.mp4?t=1732526354\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Of course, the completion of music is not everything in the game. You can lower notes, change styles, and even reverse the music! Experience music in more colorful ways through music-centric stages.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A fairytale atmosphere</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039360/extras/173915e6e51925d372aae48fe152fa79.poster.avif?t=1732526354\" width=258 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039360/extras/173915e6e51925d372aae48fe152fa79.webm?t=1732526354\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039360/extras/173915e6e51925d372aae48fe152fa79.mp4?t=1732526354\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039360/extras/a2d6a6bd09eb470d8b138aa31330c326.poster.avif?t=1732526354\" width=280 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039360/extras/a2d6a6bd09eb470d8b138aa31330c326.webm?t=1732526354\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039360/extras/a2d6a6bd09eb470d8b138aa31330c326.mp4?t=1732526354\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore surreal worlds with a cute little companion in cute graphics and dreamy melodies. Face memory and overcome adversity, become a fairytale main character!</p>",
